00:08:14.320 --> 00:08:15.510 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Did you
see that spiral--

00:08:15.510 --> 00:08:15.910 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Oh, yes.

00:08:15.910 --> 00:08:17.076 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: -as you grew older?

00:08:17.076 --> 00:08:17.810 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Oh, yes.

00:08:17.810 --> 00:08:18.930 align:middle line:90%
Unfortunately.

00:08:18.930 --> 00:08:20.940 align:middle line:84%
So he began to drink
