00:08:22.700 --> 00:08:23.283 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Sure.

00:08:23.283 --> 00:08:25.040 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: And I'm sorry
to tell you that--

00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:26.210 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Tore up the family.

00:08:26.210 --> 00:08:27.960 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: -he began to
physically abuse her.

00:08:27.960 --> 00:08:28.626 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, my.

00:08:28.626 --> 00:08:29.570 align:middle line:90%
And he had never done?

00:08:29.570 --> 00:08:30.140 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: No.

00:08:30.140 --> 00:08:34.437 align:middle line:84%
On a regular basis
between 1973 and 1975--

00:08:34.437 --> 00:08:36.770 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And you're witnessing
all this as a little boy.

00:08:36.770 --> 00:08:37.809 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Horrific.

00:08:37.809 --> 00:08:39.929 align:middle line:84%
And I have no
doubt, George, based

00:08:39.929 --> 00:08:43.860 align:middle line:84%
on what I saw that these
demonic forces were present

00:08:43.860 --> 00:08:45.790 align:middle line:84%
and they were able
to manipulate him

00:08:45.790 --> 00:08:48.290 align:middle line:84%
while under the
influence of alcohol.

00:08:48.290 --> 00:08:51.980 align:middle line:84%
And it really intensified
and fueled his rage

00:08:51.980 --> 00:08:55.190 align:middle line:84%
towards my mother while being
in these drunken stupors.

00:08:55.190 --> 00:08:58.420 align:middle line:84%
And he would say he had no
recollections of anything.

00:08:58.420 --> 00:09:01.770 align:middle line:84%
Now again, I'm not excusing
my dad for the actions

00:09:01.770 --> 00:09:05.830 align:middle line:84%
that he took; however,
the forces at work,

00:09:05.830 --> 00:09:08.990 align:middle line:84%
and there truly were
demonic forces at work here,

00:09:08.990 --> 00:09:12.700 align:middle line:84%
had a big hand in this
behavior and the steering

00:09:12.700 --> 00:09:13.510 align:middle line:90%
of this behavior.

00:09:13.510 --> 00:09:15.060 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Did he
ever come after you?

00:09:15.060 --> 00:09:17.260 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: Never once
came after me,

00:09:17.260 --> 00:09:21.530 align:middle line:84%
but the focus seemed
to be on my mother.

00:09:21.530 --> 00:09:23.120 align:middle line:84%
And I guess because
they were at odds.

00:09:23.120 --> 00:09:24.955 align:middle line:84%
You know, he would stay
out all hours of the night

00:09:24.955 --> 00:09:26.770 align:middle line:84%
and, of course, my
mother's upset by this.

00:09:26.770 --> 00:09:27.410 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Sure.

00:09:27.410 --> 00:09:31.240 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: So the focus
seemed to be on her,

00:09:31.240 --> 00:09:32.760 align:middle line:84%
but he did have
violent outbursts

00:09:32.760 --> 00:09:34.430 align:middle line:90%
towards others at times.

00:09:34.430 --> 00:09:36.820 align:middle line:84%
And it's a shame
because I loved my dad.

00:09:36.820 --> 00:09:39.190 align:middle line:90%
He was a very, very good man.

00:09:39.190 --> 00:09:41.910 align:middle line:84%
I saw him as a heroic
type of individual.

00:09:41.910 --> 00:09:46.870 align:middle line:84%
So when this shift
began, it just literally

00:09:46.870 --> 00:09:50.170 align:middle line:84%
tore me to pieces and
my perception of him.

00:09:50.170 --> 00:09:52.380 align:middle line:84%
And I'm sorry to say
that I carried a burning

00:09:52.380 --> 00:09:54.530 align:middle line:84%
hatred towards him
for many, many years

00:09:54.530 --> 00:09:57.020 align:middle line:84%
for these things that were
done and other things.

00:09:57.020 --> 00:10:01.860 align:middle line:84%
I'm happy to tell you that I was
able to eventually forgive him

00:10:01.860 --> 00:10:03.402 align:middle line:84%
and it was before
his untimely death.

00:10:03.402 --> 00:10:04.943 align:middle line:84%
You know, neither
of my parents lived

00:10:04.943 --> 00:10:06.180 align:middle line:90%
to see the age of 50, George.

00:10:06.180 --> 00:10:07.304 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's very young.

00:10:07.304 --> 00:10:08.160 align:middle line:90%
Extremely young.

00:10:08.160 --> 00:10:08.890 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Oh, yes.

00:10:08.890 --> 00:10:11.380 align:middle line:84%
And, you know, again,
I'm so thankful that I

00:10:11.380 --> 00:10:14.755 align:middle line:84%
had that opportunity to forgive
him before he left this Earth.

00:10:14.755 --> 00:10:16.380 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Made you
feel better at least.

00:10:16.380 --> 00:10:17.850 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Much, much better.

00:10:17.850 --> 00:10:19.780 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: When this
was going on, Bill,

00:10:19.780 --> 00:10:22.312 align:middle line:84%
did anybody physically
see anything?

00:10:22.312 --> 00:10:23.020 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Oh, yeah.

00:10:23.020 --> 00:10:23.770 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: They did.

00:10:23.770 --> 00:10:25.950 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Absolutely.

00:10:25.950 --> 00:10:29.350 align:middle line:84%
The first to see a
manifestation I guess maybe

00:10:29.350 --> 00:10:35.150 align:middle line:84%
would have been me at the age
of five years old in 1971.

00:10:35.150 --> 00:10:38.120 align:middle line:84%
Pretty much an experience
like my sister had.

00:10:38.120 --> 00:10:39.770 align:middle line:84%
I'm asleep in my
bed late at night.

00:10:39.770 --> 00:10:42.940 align:middle line:84%
Now, my brother and I shared
the bedroom first on the right

00:10:42.940 --> 00:10:44.800 align:middle line:90%
down the hallway.

00:10:44.800 --> 00:10:47.050 align:middle line:84%
And his bed was
closest to the window,

00:10:47.050 --> 00:10:49.890 align:middle line:84%
mine was closest to the
doorway, to the hallway.

00:10:49.890 --> 00:10:53.370 align:middle line:84%
Middle of the night, something
wakes me up from my sleep.

00:10:53.370 --> 00:10:54.530 align:middle line:90%
I can't see anything there.

00:10:54.530 --> 00:10:55.390 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: You can feel it.

00:10:55.390 --> 00:10:56.140 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: I feel it.

00:10:56.140 --> 00:10:58.810 align:middle line:84%
I feel the presence of
something, someone or something

00:10:58.810 --> 00:11:00.710 align:middle line:90%
there, so I'm unnerved.

00:11:00.710 --> 00:11:01.860 align:middle line:90%
You know, I'm scared.

00:11:01.860 --> 00:11:02.360 align:middle line:90%
I

00:11:02.360 --> 00:11:05.000 align:middle line:84%
don't see anything there, but
I know something is there.

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:06.830 align:middle line:90%
Now, I'm five years old.

00:11:06.830 --> 00:11:08.800 align:middle line:90%
So I go to get out of bed.

00:11:08.800 --> 00:11:10.730 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to go in
and get my parents.

00:11:10.730 --> 00:11:12.396 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And you
remember all this, too.

00:11:12.396 --> 00:11:14.060 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: I remember it vividly.

00:11:14.060 --> 00:11:16.540 align:middle line:84%
I could-- the trauma
level from this event

00:11:16.540 --> 00:11:18.612 align:middle line:84%
is burned into my mind
and psyche forever.

00:11:18.612 --> 00:11:20.070 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: It's etched
there forever.

00:11:20.070 --> 00:11:21.200 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Yes.

00:11:21.200 --> 00:11:24.135 align:middle line:84%
So I get out of bed, I'm going
to go in and get my parents,

00:11:24.135 --> 00:11:27.610 align:middle line:84%
and a tremendous force
grabbed me by my shoulders

00:11:27.610 --> 00:11:30.860 align:middle line:84%
and slammed me back
on the bed on my back.

00:11:30.860 --> 00:11:34.000 align:middle line:84%
George, I've given over 1,000
interviews and I'm telling you,

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:37.020 align:middle line:84%
each and every time I describe
this it gives me chills

00:11:37.020 --> 00:11:40.952 align:middle line:84%
because it was off the
charts for the trauma level.

00:11:40.952 --> 00:11:42.160 align:middle line:90%
I thought I was going to die.

00:11:42.160 --> 00:11:45.320 align:middle line:84%
I thought my heart was going
to jump out of my body.

00:11:45.320 --> 00:11:45.997 align:middle line:90%
This event--

00:11:45.997 --> 00:11:47.830 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Just went
flying back into the bed.

00:11:47.830 --> 00:11:49.246 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: And then
I felt paralyzed.

00:11:49.246 --> 00:11:50.890 align:middle line:84%
I felt like I couldn't
move anything.

00:11:50.890 --> 00:11:54.210 align:middle line:84%
The only thing that seemed
to move or work were my eyes.

00:11:54.210 --> 00:11:56.490 align:middle line:84%
Everything else, I tried to
scream out for my parents

00:11:56.490 --> 00:11:57.440 align:middle line:90%
and my mouth wouldn't even work.

00:11:57.440 --> 00:11:58.750 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: It was
holding you down.

00:11:58.750 --> 00:11:59.541 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Absolutely.

00:11:59.541 --> 00:12:00.830 align:middle line:90%
And I felt paralyzed.

00:12:00.830 --> 00:12:02.700 align:middle line:90%
I felt so helpless.

00:12:02.700 --> 00:12:05.520 align:middle line:84%
And it seemed like
it lasted for hours.

00:12:05.520 --> 00:12:07.740 align:middle line:84%
I'm sure it only lasted
for several minutes,

00:12:07.740 --> 00:12:10.150 align:middle line:84%
but a lot of things
happened in that period

00:12:10.150 --> 00:12:11.950 align:middle line:90%
of time, horrible things.

00:12:11.950 --> 00:12:16.100 align:middle line:84%
And it culminated with the
appearance of what I truly

00:12:16.100 --> 00:12:18.850 align:middle line:84%
believe was a divine
manifestation.

00:12:18.850 --> 00:12:21.770 align:middle line:84%
As all of these horrible
things were happening,

00:12:21.770 --> 00:12:26.720 align:middle line:84%
this beautiful woman suddenly
appears at the foot of my bed.

00:12:26.720 --> 00:12:27.460 align:middle line:90%
She had like an--

00:12:27.460 --> 00:12:28.430 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Angelic look?

00:12:28.430 --> 00:12:29.870 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Absolutely.

00:12:29.870 --> 00:12:34.940 align:middle line:84%
And had, I would say very
pale blue, if not white, type

00:12:34.940 --> 00:12:36.490 align:middle line:90%
of shimmering gown.

00:12:36.490 --> 00:12:39.720 align:middle line:84%
She we shimmering,
glowing, shimmering.

00:12:39.720 --> 00:12:44.232 align:middle line:84%
I felt so much love and
peace from this being

00:12:44.232 --> 00:12:46.190 align:middle line:84%
and all the horrible
things that were happening

00:12:46.190 --> 00:12:47.690 align:middle line:84%
to me suddenly stopped
with the appearance.

00:12:47.690 --> 00:12:49.270 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Maybe your
guardian angel?

00:12:49.270 --> 00:12:53.030 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: Well, here's the
most incredible thing.

00:12:53.030 --> 00:12:58.820 align:middle line:84%
As this event
culminated, the lady

00:12:58.820 --> 00:13:01.700 align:middle line:84%
turned and floated up
through the ceiling.

00:13:01.700 --> 00:13:05.850 align:middle line:84%
The most incredible part of
this was this-- what I believe

00:13:05.850 --> 00:13:08.030 align:middle line:84%
was a divine
manifestation, an angel

00:13:08.030 --> 00:13:13.090 align:middle line:84%
if you will-- looked
exactly like my mother.

00:13:13.090 --> 00:13:14.020 align:middle line:90%
Exactly.

00:13:14.020 --> 00:13:15.890 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Now, she wasn't dead
at the time though, was she?

00:13:15.890 --> 00:13:16.390 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: No.

00:13:16.390 --> 00:13:19.920 align:middle line:84%
I got-- after this ended,
I was out of breath.

00:13:19.920 --> 00:13:22.610 align:middle line:84%
I was so traumatized,
I was sweating.

00:13:22.610 --> 00:13:24.834 align:middle line:90%
I ran in, woke my parents up.

00:13:24.834 --> 00:13:26.750 align:middle line:84%
Of course, my dad, he
didn't want any of that.

00:13:26.750 --> 00:13:29.420 align:middle line:10%
But my mom, she went
back in with me.

00:13:29.420 --> 00:13:30.670 align:middle line:10%
>>NOORY: Yeah, to comfort you.

00:13:30.670 --> 00:13:33.590 align:middle line:10%
>>BEAN: But I said to her, how
did you get in here so fast?

00:13:33.590 --> 00:13:34.170 align:middle line:90%
That's what I said to her.

00:13:34.170 --> 00:13:35.000 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: You thought it was her.

00:13:35.000 --> 00:13:37.041 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: And she said, what
are you talking about?

00:13:37.041 --> 00:13:41.480 align:middle line:84%
And so as the years progressed,
and those attacks happened

00:13:41.480 --> 00:13:45.290 align:middle line:84%
to me many, many times over
the years of living in there,

00:13:45.290 --> 00:13:49.170 align:middle line:84%
and each and every time, George,
after the event would happen,

00:13:49.170 --> 00:13:50.539 align:middle line:90%
I would feel like I had the flu.

00:13:50.539 --> 00:13:51.830 align:middle line:90%
I would have these high fevers.

00:13:51.830 --> 00:13:52.520 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yeah.

00:13:52.520 --> 00:13:55.700 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: The body aches and
all this kind of stuff.

