00:16:31.440 --> 00:16:34.140 align:middle line:84%
and they used to gather and
worship at this structure

00:16:34.140 --> 00:16:35.141 align:middle line:90%
called the Wishing Rock.

00:16:35.141 --> 00:16:36.306 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's interesting.

00:16:36.306 --> 00:16:38.380 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: And they said
that the Wishing Rock was

00:16:38.380 --> 00:16:40.870 align:middle line:84%
some sort of gateway
or portal and it

00:16:40.870 --> 00:16:42.470 align:middle line:90%
had these supernatural powers.

00:16:42.470 --> 00:16:45.490 align:middle line:84%
Now if there's anything
to this at all,

00:16:45.490 --> 00:16:48.000 align:middle line:84%
then it is possible
that these entities

00:16:48.000 --> 00:16:49.830 align:middle line:90%
came through that portal.

00:16:49.830 --> 00:16:52.570 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What an amazing story.

00:16:52.570 --> 00:16:54.820 align:middle line:84%
So your dad, while
this is going on

00:16:54.820 --> 00:16:59.630 align:middle line:84%
and these demons, I'll call them
demons, are all over the place,

00:16:59.630 --> 00:17:02.110 align:middle line:84%
he just abruptly
leaves the family?

00:17:02.110 --> 00:17:05.089 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: Well, again, it was part
of the downward spiral, George.

00:17:05.089 --> 00:17:07.880 align:middle line:84%
It's so sad and tragic because
my dad was such a good man

00:17:07.880 --> 00:17:09.390 align:middle line:90%
and he was blessed with every--

00:17:09.390 --> 00:17:10.790 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: And you saw this thing.

00:17:10.790 --> 00:17:13.410 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: He was blessed with
every physical attribute

00:17:13.410 --> 00:17:16.020 align:middle line:84%
necessary to be highly
successful in life.

00:17:16.020 --> 00:17:17.140 align:middle line:90%
He should have flourished.

00:17:17.140 --> 00:17:19.040 align:middle line:84%
We should have flourished
with him as a family.

00:17:19.040 --> 00:17:19.831 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Of course.

00:17:19.831 --> 00:17:20.530 align:middle line:90%
Of course.

00:17:20.530 --> 00:17:23.119 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: So when he began
this heavy drinking,

00:17:23.119 --> 00:17:24.940 align:middle line:84%
it just started the
downward spiral.

00:17:24.940 --> 00:17:27.520 align:middle line:84%
His business began to fail
because he had just pretty

00:17:27.520 --> 00:17:28.020 align:middle line:90%
much--

00:17:28.020 --> 00:17:30.103 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: He was probably
unreliable at that point.

00:17:30.103 --> 00:17:31.240 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Absolutely.

00:17:31.240 --> 00:17:32.800 align:middle line:90%
Had given up on everything.

00:17:32.800 --> 00:17:37.240 align:middle line:84%
And then not only with the
domestic abuse with my mom,

00:17:37.240 --> 00:17:40.000 align:middle line:90%
he was having other issues.

00:17:40.000 --> 00:17:41.870 align:middle line:84%
Owed people money,
his employees,

00:17:41.870 --> 00:17:43.620 align:middle line:90%
and things of that nature.

00:17:43.620 --> 00:17:44.910 align:middle line:90%
You name it.

00:17:44.910 --> 00:17:47.700 align:middle line:84%
It was horrible, the things
that were going wrong.

00:17:47.700 --> 00:17:51.800 align:middle line:84%
And I guess finally he
just-- one day he just left.

00:17:51.800 --> 00:17:55.030 align:middle line:84%
And he went,
relocated in Florida.

00:17:55.030 --> 00:17:57.565 align:middle line:84%
Went down there with his older
brother, my uncle Clifford,

00:17:57.565 --> 00:18:00.020 align:middle line:90%
who is a very devout Christian.

00:18:00.020 --> 00:18:02.647 align:middle line:84%
And my dad had a battle
for the rest of his life.

00:18:02.647 --> 00:18:04.480 align:middle line:84%
He went down there and
he would have periods

00:18:04.480 --> 00:18:07.160 align:middle line:84%
to where he would do good and
stay away from the drinking,

00:18:07.160 --> 00:18:08.660 align:middle line:84%
and then he would
have periods where

00:18:08.660 --> 00:18:10.010 align:middle line:90%
you would revert back to that.

00:18:10.010 --> 00:18:11.320 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Did you stay
in touch with him?

00:18:11.320 --> 00:18:13.650 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: Well, I'm sorry
say, during that time period

00:18:13.650 --> 00:18:16.840 align:middle line:84%
I very much hated my father
and I didn't want anything

00:18:16.840 --> 00:18:20.350 align:middle line:84%
to do with him;
however, a blessing

00:18:20.350 --> 00:18:25.000 align:middle line:84%
came in 1979 when my brother,
who unconditionally loved

00:18:25.000 --> 00:18:27.800 align:middle line:84%
my dad, wanted to take
a trip to Florida.

00:18:27.800 --> 00:18:29.820 align:middle line:84%
I did not want to go,
but I ended up going.

00:18:29.820 --> 00:18:32.320 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And how many years had
been since you had seen him?

00:18:32.320 --> 00:18:34.077 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: It had been
probably four years.

00:18:34.077 --> 00:18:34.660 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yeah.

00:18:34.660 --> 00:18:35.349 align:middle line:90%
Long time.

00:18:35.349 --> 00:18:35.890 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Yeah.

00:18:35.890 --> 00:18:38.590 align:middle line:84%
And so I really still
didn't want to see him,

00:18:38.590 --> 00:18:40.460 align:middle line:84%
but I went with
my little brother.

00:18:40.460 --> 00:18:42.490 align:middle line:84%
Ended up being a
tremendous blessing.

00:18:42.490 --> 00:18:44.780 align:middle line:84%
And the reason the trip
ended up being a blessing

00:18:44.780 --> 00:18:48.820 align:middle line:84%
is because my uncle Cliff had
a talk with me about faith.

00:18:48.820 --> 00:18:53.190 align:middle line:84%
And about if we had
faith, God would--

00:18:53.190 --> 00:18:54.367 align:middle line:90%
we could connect with God.

00:18:54.367 --> 00:18:55.450 align:middle line:90%
He would hear our prayers.

00:18:55.450 --> 00:18:56.784 align:middle line:90%
He would feel our faith.

00:18:56.784 --> 00:18:59.200 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: He's the one who got
you kind of straightened out

00:18:59.200 --> 00:18:59.960 align:middle line:90%
it sounds like.

00:18:59.960 --> 00:19:02.000 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: It was invaluable.

00:19:02.000 --> 00:19:04.920 align:middle line:84%
That advice and that
conversation I had with him,

00:19:04.920 --> 00:19:07.610 align:middle line:84%
that was the beginning of the
planting of the seeds for where

00:19:07.610 --> 00:19:09.540 align:middle line:84%
I'm at right now in being
a spiritual warrior.

00:19:09.540 --> 00:19:11.290 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: It was the
epiphany in your life.

00:19:11.290 --> 00:19:11.790 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Yes.

00:19:11.790 --> 00:19:14.190 align:middle line:84%
George, I could not be here
now had I not been there.

00:19:14.190 --> 00:19:16.640 align:middle line:84%
So God does work
in mysterious ways,

00:19:16.640 --> 00:19:20.040 align:middle line:84%
and that teaching
was invaluable.

00:19:20.040 --> 00:19:23.240 align:middle line:84%
Little did I know
that on the very day

00:19:23.240 --> 00:19:25.100 align:middle line:84%
I would come back
from that trip,

00:19:25.100 --> 00:19:28.390 align:middle line:84%
I would engage in spiritual
warfare for the first time

00:19:28.390 --> 00:19:30.840 align:middle line:84%
against these entities
that had attacked us

00:19:30.840 --> 00:19:33.429 align:middle line:84%
for so long, oppressed
us for so long.

00:19:33.429 --> 00:19:35.470 align:middle line:84%
Because I'll tell you,
George, it got unbearable.

00:19:35.470 --> 00:19:42.180 align:middle line:84%
After my dad left, my mother
began having physical attacks

00:19:42.180 --> 00:19:44.880 align:middle line:90%
from two entities in particular.

00:19:44.880 --> 00:19:48.294 align:middle line:84%
And my mother had cuts, bruises,
and scratches on her long

00:19:48.294 --> 00:19:49.210 align:middle line:90%
after my dad had left.

00:19:49.210 --> 00:19:51.381 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You probably
figured is dad back here?

00:19:51.381 --> 00:19:52.380 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: It was horrific.

00:19:52.380 --> 00:19:54.338 align:middle line:84%
She couldn't-- it got to
the point to where she

00:19:54.338 --> 00:19:56.880 align:middle line:84%
couldn't sleep in
her bed anymore.

00:19:56.880 --> 00:20:00.300 align:middle line:84%
They were coming to her
bed, they were choking her.

00:20:00.300 --> 00:20:02.730 align:middle line:84%
They were hitting
her, scratching her,

00:20:02.730 --> 00:20:05.120 align:middle line:84%
and one occasion,
she was being choked

00:20:05.120 --> 00:20:08.850 align:middle line:84%
by this entity in black,
black hair, black beard,

00:20:08.850 --> 00:20:10.640 align:middle line:90%
had a black suit on.

00:20:10.640 --> 00:20:13.680 align:middle line:84%
The eyes were even black,
and chalky white skin.

00:20:13.680 --> 00:20:15.930 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: They wanted to
do something bad to her.

00:20:15.930 --> 00:20:17.290 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: No question about it.

00:20:17.290 --> 00:20:21.300 align:middle line:84%
So after the episode is over,
my mother is gasping for air,

00:20:21.300 --> 00:20:22.862 align:middle line:90%
she gets out of bed.

00:20:22.862 --> 00:20:24.820 align:middle line:84%
Now she's got to go all
the way up the hallway.

00:20:24.820 --> 00:20:26.119 align:middle line:90%
She wants to get water.

00:20:26.119 --> 00:20:27.910 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And your dad
is gone by this time?

00:20:27.910 --> 00:20:28.630 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Gone.

00:20:28.630 --> 00:20:30.810 align:middle line:90%
This is after my dad had left.

00:20:30.810 --> 00:20:33.800 align:middle line:84%
So she's gasping for
air, she wants water.

00:20:33.800 --> 00:20:36.380 align:middle line:84%
She goes into the
kitchen to get a glass.

00:20:36.380 --> 00:20:41.210 align:middle line:84%
So she opens the cabinet
door, and an unseen force,

00:20:41.210 --> 00:20:43.740 align:middle line:84%
like a projectile,
shot a glass out that

00:20:43.740 --> 00:20:47.450 align:middle line:84%
struck my mother above the
eye, split her eye wide open,

00:20:47.450 --> 00:20:48.610 align:middle line:90%
knocked her unconscious.

00:20:48.610 --> 00:20:50.080 align:middle line:84%
She had be taken
to the hospital.

00:20:50.080 --> 00:20:50.930 align:middle line:90%
She had to get stitches.

00:20:50.930 --> 00:20:51.530 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: She could
have gone blind.

00:20:51.530 --> 00:20:52.260 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Yes.

00:20:52.260 --> 00:20:56.750 align:middle line:84%
So this is the type of
attack that we were under.

00:20:56.750 --> 00:21:00.130 align:middle line:84%
And make no mistake,
when I say attack,

00:21:00.130 --> 00:21:05.010 align:middle line:84%
I mean true, all out physical,
mental, and spiritual attack.

00:21:05.010 --> 00:21:07.660 align:middle line:84%
My family was
absolutely decimated

00:21:07.660 --> 00:21:08.746 align:middle line:90%
by these demonic forces.

00:21:08.746 --> 00:21:10.370 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Is that
unusual, Bill, to have

00:21:10.370 --> 00:21:12.580 align:middle line:90%
those attacks that violent?

00:21:12.580 --> 00:21:14.260 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Highly unusual.

00:21:14.260 --> 00:21:15.732 align:middle line:84%
You know, I have
to say, since I've

00:21:15.732 --> 00:21:17.190 align:middle line:84%
become a deliverance
minister, I've

00:21:17.190 --> 00:21:18.660 align:middle line:90%
traveled all over this country.

00:21:18.660 --> 00:21:20.550 align:middle line:84%
God has worked through
me to help many people

00:21:20.550 --> 00:21:23.240 align:middle line:84%
and I'm forever
grateful for that.

00:21:23.240 --> 00:21:27.830 align:middle line:84%
I can honestly tell you, George,
that I have never encountered

00:21:27.830 --> 00:21:30.920 align:middle line:84%
a case to the
severity of the case

00:21:30.920 --> 00:21:34.010 align:middle line:90%
that my family and I endured.

00:21:34.010 --> 00:21:36.670 align:middle line:84%
And I'm thankful for
those people that I've--

00:21:36.670 --> 00:21:39.170 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I'm amazed that you've
turned out the way you have.

00:21:39.170 --> 00:21:40.170 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: It's God.

00:21:40.170 --> 00:21:41.120 align:middle line:90%
Truly it is.

00:21:41.120 --> 00:21:44.380 align:middle line:84%
This is God's
doing, because I've

00:21:44.380 --> 00:21:46.330 align:middle line:84%
been in many
life-threatening situations

00:21:46.330 --> 00:21:47.880 align:middle line:84%
during the course
of my lifetime.

00:21:47.880 --> 00:21:50.790 align:middle line:84%
Yet, God made a way to
spare me each and every time

00:21:50.790 --> 00:21:54.640 align:middle line:84%
for this very moment now
and for this very time frame

00:21:54.640 --> 00:21:57.430 align:middle line:84%
that I'm in with God
working through me to help

00:21:57.430 --> 00:21:58.070 align:middle line:90%
these people.

00:21:58.070 --> 00:22:00.028 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I want to, on
our next "Beyond Belief"

00:22:00.028 --> 00:22:02.540 align:middle line:84%
show, really get into
what you do for people

00:22:02.540 --> 00:22:04.240 align:middle line:90%
and how you do this.

00:22:04.240 --> 00:22:06.350 align:middle line:84%
When you were on with
me on the radio show,

00:22:06.350 --> 00:22:09.550 align:middle line:84%
we talked a little bit about
your father and a headless boy

00:22:09.550 --> 00:22:10.225 align:middle line:90%
on a porch.

00:22:10.225 --> 00:22:11.225 align:middle line:90%
You remember that story?

00:22:11.225 --> 00:22:11.670 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Yeah.

00:22:11.670 --> 00:22:12.720 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What was
that all about?

00:22:12.720 --> 00:22:14.553 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: Well, that was
my uncle, Mike Zonek,

00:22:14.553 --> 00:22:17.970 align:middle line:84%
and that photo was
taken in the '50s.

00:22:17.970 --> 00:22:20.240 align:middle line:84%
Now, I never knew these
photos existed, George,

00:22:20.240 --> 00:22:22.170 align:middle line:90%
until after my mother's death.

00:22:22.170 --> 00:22:25.820 align:middle line:84%
And we endured 10
years in that house.

00:22:25.820 --> 00:22:28.167 align:middle line:84%
We had a priest involved
for the last 16 months

00:22:28.167 --> 00:22:29.000 align:middle line:90%
that we lived there.

00:22:29.000 --> 00:22:32.120 align:middle line:84%
Shortly after my mother--
two tragedies had occurred.

00:22:32.120 --> 00:22:33.750 align:middle line:84%
My beloved grandmother,
Dora Harvey,

00:22:33.750 --> 00:22:35.850 align:middle line:84%
had passed from a sudden
series of heart attacks.

00:22:35.850 --> 00:22:37.750 align:middle line:84%
And two months and
two days later,

00:22:37.750 --> 00:22:39.340 align:middle line:84%
my beloved mother,
Patricia Bean,

00:22:39.340 --> 00:22:42.510 align:middle line:84%
had died from a cerebral
hemorrhage at the age of 44.

00:22:42.510 --> 00:22:45.550 align:middle line:84%
George, I'm telling you as
sure as I'm looking at you,

00:22:45.550 --> 00:22:47.940 align:middle line:84%
I have no doubt that
these demonic forces had

00:22:47.940 --> 00:22:49.830 align:middle line:84%
a hand in both of those
deaths because they

00:22:49.830 --> 00:22:53.770 align:middle line:84%
were both under so much
stress and pressure.

00:22:53.770 --> 00:22:56.230 align:middle line:84%
So the reason I'm
telling you this

00:22:56.230 --> 00:22:59.300 align:middle line:84%
is because my mother had a
photo collection, which I never

00:22:59.300 --> 00:23:00.680 align:middle line:90%
saw back then.

00:23:00.680 --> 00:23:04.010 align:middle line:84%
After she had passed, many
years after she had passed,

00:23:04.010 --> 00:23:06.470 align:middle line:84%
my wife and I were
at my sister's house

00:23:06.470 --> 00:23:07.917 align:middle line:90%
Christmas of 2005.

00:23:07.917 --> 00:23:09.500 align:middle line:84%
My sister said, would
you like to have

00:23:09.500 --> 00:23:11.280 align:middle line:90%
some of mom's old family photos?

00:23:11.280 --> 00:23:12.650 align:middle line:90%
And I said yes.

00:23:12.650 --> 00:23:14.340 align:middle line:84%
I started going
through the photographs

00:23:14.340 --> 00:23:16.480 align:middle line:90%
and that was one of the photos.

00:23:16.480 --> 00:23:20.370 align:middle line:84%
And it is an amazing
photograph, to say the least.

00:23:20.370 --> 00:23:23.390 align:middle line:84%
Now on the surface,
one would think, OK,

00:23:23.390 --> 00:23:24.980 align:middle line:90%
that's a double exposure.

00:23:24.980 --> 00:23:26.700 align:middle line:90%
What's the big deal?

00:23:26.700 --> 00:23:29.850 align:middle line:84%
I want people to take a very
close look at that photograph

00:23:29.850 --> 00:23:34.152 align:middle line:84%
because, first of all, you see
like this black blob shadow

00:23:34.152 --> 00:23:34.860 align:middle line:90%
image beside him.

00:23:34.860 --> 00:23:35.400 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yeah, what is that?

00:23:35.400 --> 00:23:36.730 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: I have no idea.

00:23:36.730 --> 00:23:39.610 align:middle line:84%
But secondly, you see two
children in front of him.

00:23:39.610 --> 00:23:40.530 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Ghoulish.

00:23:40.530 --> 00:23:41.030 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Yes.

00:23:41.030 --> 00:23:44.680 align:middle line:84%
The first one
doesn't have a head.

00:23:44.680 --> 00:23:48.062 align:middle line:84%
Now if you closer, look over
on that step right there.

00:23:48.062 --> 00:23:50.020 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Bill, something
happened at that house

00:23:50.020 --> 00:23:50.720 align:middle line:90%
a long time ago.

00:23:50.720 --> 00:23:52.370 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: No question about it.

00:23:52.370 --> 00:23:55.410 align:middle line:84%
I really think, without truly
knowing the answer, George,

00:23:55.410 --> 00:23:59.930 align:middle line:84%
my best guesstimation
and my gut tells me

00:23:59.930 --> 00:24:04.350 align:middle line:84%
that something horrific
happened in the entire area,

00:24:04.350 --> 00:24:06.620 align:middle line:84%
whether Native American
land was disturbed

00:24:06.620 --> 00:24:08.430 align:middle line:90%
or whatever it may be.

00:24:08.430 --> 00:24:10.090 align:middle line:84%
Because, again,
we have the factor

00:24:10.090 --> 00:24:12.790 align:middle line:84%
of all these other homes
that have had these problems.

00:24:12.790 --> 00:24:16.050 align:middle line:84%
Not to the severity that
my family and I did,

00:24:16.050 --> 00:24:18.287 align:middle line:84%
but we do still
have it nonetheless.

00:24:18.287 --> 00:24:18.870 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Sure.

00:24:18.870 --> 00:24:20.150 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: So, yeah.

00:24:20.150 --> 00:24:24.400 align:middle line:84%
Something did take place
there to really stir this up.

00:24:24.400 --> 00:24:27.580 align:middle line:84%
And then you couple
that with the conjuring

00:24:27.580 --> 00:24:29.920 align:middle line:84%
by that family
member, and you had

00:24:29.920 --> 00:24:31.574 align:middle line:90%
this incredible storm of evil.

00:24:31.574 --> 00:24:33.990 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And your dad died,
you said, at a young age, too.

00:24:33.990 --> 00:24:35.739 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: My dad was
shot to death in 1987--

00:24:35.739 --> 00:24:36.600 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, my God.

00:24:36.600 --> 00:24:38.260 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: -at the age of 48.

00:24:38.260 --> 00:24:40.060 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Was his
drinking because of that?

00:24:40.060 --> 00:24:40.850 align:middle line:90%
Or was he robbed?

00:24:40.850 --> 00:24:41.570 align:middle line:90%
Or what happened?

00:24:41.570 --> 00:24:43.410 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Well, it had a factor.

00:24:43.410 --> 00:24:46.580 align:middle line:84%
It was a domestic
issue, so the drinking

00:24:46.580 --> 00:24:48.340 align:middle line:84%
did play a role
in it, although he

00:24:48.340 --> 00:24:50.704 align:middle line:84%
wasn't under the influence
of alcohol at the time.

00:24:50.704 --> 00:24:51.620 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: At that time.

00:24:51.620 --> 00:24:53.990 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: He had actually--
the ironic thing

00:24:53.990 --> 00:24:56.940 align:middle line:84%
is that he was going
through one of those periods

00:24:56.940 --> 00:25:00.340 align:middle line:84%
to where he was straightening
his life up again,

00:25:00.340 --> 00:25:02.730 align:middle line:84%
and he had stopped the
drinking for several weeks.

00:25:02.730 --> 00:25:04.130 align:middle line:90%
And, I feel worse for my--

00:25:04.130 --> 00:25:05.770 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: So you thought he
was pulling himself together?

00:25:05.770 --> 00:25:06.269 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Yes.

00:25:06.269 --> 00:25:08.220 align:middle line:84%
And I feel worse for
my brother than anybody

00:25:08.220 --> 00:25:13.060 align:middle line:84%
because my brother is nearly
three years younger than I.

00:25:13.060 --> 00:25:16.234 align:middle line:84%
He was so young when my mother
passed, and many family members

00:25:16.234 --> 00:25:16.900 align:middle line:90%
as well, George.

00:25:16.900 --> 00:25:18.191 align:middle line:90%
I have very little family left.

00:25:18.191 --> 00:25:20.720 align:middle line:84%
We've lost many family members
under bizarre circumstances.

00:25:20.720 --> 00:25:21.920 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: We're your
family now, Bill.

00:25:21.920 --> 00:25:22.711 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Absolutely.

00:25:22.711 --> 00:25:25.710 align:middle line:90%
And I praise God for you.

00:25:25.710 --> 00:25:28.360 align:middle line:84%
But my brother was
living with my father

00:25:28.360 --> 00:25:29.537 align:middle line:90%
at the time in Florida.

00:25:29.537 --> 00:25:30.370 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, my God.

00:25:30.370 --> 00:25:32.328 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: So he's already
gone through this thing

00:25:32.328 --> 00:25:33.870 align:middle line:84%
with my mother,
and then my father

00:25:33.870 --> 00:25:36.340 align:middle line:84%
leaves one Sunday morning,
says, I'll be right back.

00:25:36.340 --> 00:25:37.842 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to the store.

00:25:37.842 --> 00:25:38.800 align:middle line:90%
And he never came back.

00:25:38.800 --> 00:25:40.258 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: He gets
shot in the store?

00:25:40.258 --> 00:25:42.990 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: No, he actually-- it
was a domestic-related matter

00:25:42.990 --> 00:25:44.850 align:middle line:90%
so it wasn't far from the store.

00:25:44.850 --> 00:25:47.410 align:middle line:84%
But the next thing you know
there's a police officer coming

00:25:47.410 --> 00:25:49.640 align:middle line:84%
to the door informing
my brother, who I think

00:25:49.640 --> 00:25:51.320 align:middle line:90%
was 17 at the time, that--

00:25:51.320 --> 00:25:52.570 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: He was shot to death.

00:25:52.570 --> 00:25:54.028 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: He was shot
to death, yeah.

00:25:54.028 --> 00:25:55.162 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Were you in shock?

00:25:55.162 --> 00:25:56.120 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: I was in shock.

00:25:56.120 --> 00:25:57.536 align:middle line:84%
And I was living
here in Maryland,

00:25:57.536 --> 00:25:59.590 align:middle line:84%
my brother was living
in Florida with him.

00:25:59.590 --> 00:26:01.290 align:middle line:84%
And I had come home
late one night,

00:26:01.290 --> 00:26:05.050 align:middle line:84%
and I was living with my uncle
then, and he had a note for me

00:26:05.050 --> 00:26:07.550 align:middle line:84%
on the table wake him up
no matter what time it was.

00:26:07.550 --> 00:26:09.480 align:middle line:84%
And this is like 3
o'clock in the morning,

00:26:09.480 --> 00:26:10.710 align:middle line:90%
so I knew it wasn't good.

00:26:10.710 --> 00:26:11.100 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yeah.

00:26:11.100 --> 00:26:12.225 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: And I wake him up--

00:26:12.225 --> 00:26:14.030 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You hate
those kinds of moments.

00:26:14.030 --> 00:26:15.530 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: -and he
informed me of that.

00:26:15.530 --> 00:26:19.770 align:middle line:84%
And, very much like my mother
as well, I was in zombie state.

00:26:19.770 --> 00:26:22.290 align:middle line:90%
I just-- I couldn't process it.

00:26:22.290 --> 00:26:25.120 align:middle line:84%
It took several weeks
for it to sink in

00:26:25.120 --> 00:26:27.280 align:middle line:84%
that it had really
occurred, you know.

00:26:27.280 --> 00:26:30.677 align:middle line:84%
And then I guess it
leaves such a void.

00:26:30.677 --> 00:26:33.010 align:middle line:84%
And with my mother-- you know
my mother and grandmother,

00:26:33.010 --> 00:26:35.450 align:middle line:84%
they were the two closest
people to me in my life

00:26:35.450 --> 00:26:40.470 align:middle line:84%
so when they passed, I was
just dark and empty and bitter

00:26:40.470 --> 00:26:43.220 align:middle line:90%
and in so much pain and turmoil.

00:26:43.220 --> 00:26:46.000 align:middle line:84%
Now outwardly, if you were
to talk to me back then,

00:26:46.000 --> 00:26:49.030 align:middle line:84%
I'd be cordial, but I kept
everybody at a distance

00:26:49.030 --> 00:26:51.700 align:middle line:84%
because I was in so much
pain I couldn't allow anyone

00:26:51.700 --> 00:26:52.960 align:middle line:90%
to get close to me.

00:26:52.960 --> 00:26:53.460 align:middle line:90%
I lived--

00:26:53.460 --> 00:26:54.160 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: I don't blame you.

00:26:54.160 --> 00:26:56.310 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: I lived that
way for so long, George,

00:26:56.310 --> 00:26:59.150 align:middle line:84%
and then God began this
transformation in my life.

00:26:59.150 --> 00:27:03.639 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Once this anger left in
you, did you see things change?

00:27:03.639 --> 00:27:04.430 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Absolutely.

00:27:04.430 --> 00:27:08.330 align:middle line:84%
And furthermore, I feel that
each and every one of us

00:27:08.330 --> 00:27:13.300 align:middle line:84%
in the family were under demonic
oppression at various times.

00:27:13.300 --> 00:27:15.400 align:middle line:84%
And I think during
that time frame,

00:27:15.400 --> 00:27:17.300 align:middle line:84%
I was very much under
demonic oppression

00:27:17.300 --> 00:27:19.500 align:middle line:84%
because I can
recall days, George,

00:27:19.500 --> 00:27:22.940 align:middle line:84%
that I would just
get up in the morning

00:27:22.940 --> 00:27:26.050 align:middle line:84%
and maybe use the bathroom
and come back and sit

00:27:26.050 --> 00:27:30.649 align:middle line:84%
in a dark, silent room until
it was time to go to bed.

00:27:30.649 --> 00:27:31.190 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Wow.

00:27:31.190 --> 00:27:33.600 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: In silence and darkness.

00:27:33.600 --> 00:27:37.720 align:middle line:84%
I did that so many times
because I was in so much pain,

00:27:37.720 --> 00:27:41.380 align:middle line:84%
and I really felt that the
enemy had a grip on my life

00:27:41.380 --> 00:27:42.130 align:middle line:90%
at that time.

00:27:42.130 --> 00:27:43.599 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Were you petrified?

00:27:43.599 --> 00:27:46.140 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: More like I was seeking
death, to be honest with you.

00:27:46.140 --> 00:27:49.610 align:middle line:84%
I was in so much pain, I
didn't want to live anymore.

00:27:49.610 --> 00:27:51.180 align:middle line:90%
I couldn't relate to anybody.

00:27:51.180 --> 00:27:52.790 align:middle line:90%
It affected my relationships.

00:27:52.790 --> 00:27:54.700 align:middle line:84%
I couldn't let anybody
get close to me.

00:27:54.700 --> 00:27:57.450 align:middle line:84%
So really I was, without
slitting my own wrist

00:27:57.450 --> 00:28:01.430 align:middle line:84%
or anything like that, I
was seeking ways to die,

00:28:01.430 --> 00:28:04.600 align:middle line:84%
and I was living very,
very recklessly in my life.

00:28:04.600 --> 00:28:06.650 align:middle line:84%
I've been in many
life-threatening situations,

00:28:06.650 --> 00:28:10.677 align:middle line:84%
but yet here I am today a
walking miracle from God.

00:28:10.677 --> 00:28:11.260 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: True.

00:28:11.260 --> 00:28:11.760 align:middle line:90%
No doubt.

00:28:11.760 --> 00:28:14.190 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAN: If God could
transform my life in the way

00:28:14.190 --> 00:28:17.560 align:middle line:84%
that he has and working through
me in the way that he does now,

00:28:17.560 --> 00:28:20.040 align:middle line:84%
he can do that for anyone
who will call on him.

00:28:20.040 --> 00:28:20.930 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Well, there's
a mission for you.

00:28:20.930 --> 00:28:22.054 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Absolutely, George.

00:28:22.054 --> 00:28:23.060 align:middle line:90%
It is my mission.

00:28:23.060 --> 00:28:26.300 align:middle line:84%
So again, I had to go
through those things

00:28:26.300 --> 00:28:29.720 align:middle line:84%
and experience those things
to be where I'm at now.

00:28:29.720 --> 00:28:31.880 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I want to talk
on our next program

00:28:31.880 --> 00:28:35.160 align:middle line:84%
about some of the things you
do with people to get them out

00:28:35.160 --> 00:28:39.750 align:middle line:84%
of that same rut that you were
in with those demonic forces,

00:28:39.750 --> 00:28:41.040 align:middle line:90%
and they're out there.

00:28:41.040 --> 00:28:43.180 align:middle line:90%
But what do they want, Bill?

00:28:43.180 --> 00:28:46.150 align:middle line:84%
What do these bad,
dark forces want?

00:28:46.150 --> 00:28:46.947 align:middle line:90%
Our souls?

00:28:46.947 --> 00:28:47.780 align:middle line:90%
What are they after?

00:28:47.780 --> 00:28:49.880 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: They want everything.

00:28:49.880 --> 00:28:53.000 align:middle line:90%
God, Yahweh created us.

00:28:53.000 --> 00:28:54.040 align:middle line:90%
He loves us.

00:28:54.040 --> 00:28:57.390 align:middle line:84%
And when he created us, he
left a little piece of himself

00:28:57.390 --> 00:28:59.700 align:middle line:84%
inside of each and
every one of us.

00:28:59.700 --> 00:29:03.880 align:middle line:84%
The enemy knows this, so he
tries to keep us from God,

00:29:03.880 --> 00:29:06.750 align:middle line:84%
and he confuses us and
he kind of muddies up

00:29:06.750 --> 00:29:08.960 align:middle line:84%
the communication
between ourselves

00:29:08.960 --> 00:29:13.040 align:middle line:84%
and God, Yahshua,
Jesus the Christ.

00:29:13.040 --> 00:29:15.860 align:middle line:84%
That name Yahshua
means Yahweh saves.

00:29:15.860 --> 00:29:18.590 align:middle line:84%
So God saves through
Yahshua, Jesus the Christ.

00:29:18.590 --> 00:29:19.900 align:middle line:90%
Again, the enemy knows this.

00:29:19.900 --> 00:29:22.440 align:middle line:84%
When I'm in
spiritual warfare, we

00:29:22.440 --> 00:29:27.400 align:middle line:84%
see in the Bible Yahweh's
name was listed 6,823 times,

00:29:27.400 --> 00:29:29.620 align:middle line:84%
and it was covered up
by the title of Lord.

00:29:29.620 --> 00:29:32.290 align:middle line:10%
So wherever you see Lord in
caps, it should say Yahweh.

00:29:32.290 --> 00:29:33.970 align:middle line:10%
So when I'm in battle,
I'll say, Yahweh

00:29:33.970 --> 00:29:35.274 align:middle line:10%
rebuke thee in Jesus name.

00:29:35.274 --> 00:29:36.190 align:middle line:10%
>>NOORY: And it helps?

00:29:36.190 --> 00:29:38.431 align:middle line:10%
>>BEAN: Oh, it-- they
instantly have to go.

00:29:38.431 --> 00:29:40.680 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Bill, if people
want more information on you,

00:29:40.680 --> 00:29:41.790 align:middle line:90%
where do they go?

00:29:41.790 --> 00:29:45.320 align:middle line:10%
>>BEAN: They can
visit www.billbean.net

00:29:45.320 --> 00:29:48.422 align:middle line:10%
or www.billbeanministries.com.

00:29:48.422 --> 00:29:52.210 align:middle line:10%
Whichever site you go to
is linked to the other.

00:29:52.210 --> 00:29:54.230 align:middle line:84%
Again, I answer
every single message.

00:29:54.230 --> 00:29:57.870 align:middle line:84%
George, I'm up till 4 or 5 AM
in the morning every morning

00:29:57.870 --> 00:29:59.530 align:middle line:84%
answering messages
from people in need.

00:29:59.530 --> 00:30:00.800 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And listening
to "Coast to Coast."

00:30:00.800 --> 00:30:01.600 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Of course.

00:30:01.600 --> 00:30:01.970 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Perfect.

00:30:01.970 --> 00:30:02.990 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: That's my favorite show.

00:30:02.990 --> 00:30:04.410 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Bill, thanks for
being on "Beyond Belief."

00:30:04.410 --> 00:30:05.601 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAN: Oh, my pleasure.

00:30:05.601 --> 00:30:06.350 align:middle line:90%
Thank you, George.

